Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.08,0:20:43.62,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}光が届かない場所で
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.96,0:20:52.10,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}ひとり何か探していたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.84,0:20:59.93,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}杖を握るその強さは
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.93,0:21:06.36,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}僕に少しもなかったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.92,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}遠くで声が響く
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.28,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}届かない夢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.44,0:21:18.09,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}僕が僕である限り　終わらない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.09,0:21:25.37,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}前を向いて歩いてく
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.48,0:21:34.20,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}悲しみを超えてその向こう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.76,0:21:39.96,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}怯えながら剣で織り上げた
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.80,0:21:47.39,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}影の中でも希望信じて
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.39,0:21:55.47,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}この場所で未来を変えていくから
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.39,0:21:55.47,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3\fscx60\fscy60\pos(1616,-3.2)}あす
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.23,0:22:04.17,ED_JP_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}何度でも立ち上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:43.62,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}在光照不到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:52.10,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}我独自寻觅着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.84,0:20:59.93,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}持杖所需的那份坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:06.36,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}我从未拥有一分一毫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.92,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}远方回响着呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.28,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}遥不可及的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:18.09,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}只要我还是我 便不会终结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.09,0:21:25.37,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}朝着前方迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:34.20,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}跨越悲伤 向着彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:39.96,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}心怀胆怯 以剑织路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:47.39,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}即便身陷暗影也坚信希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:55.47,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}因为我将在此处改写明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:04.17,ED_CN_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(220,220)\fax-0.1\blur3}无论多少次我都会再站起来
